Package: rsortie
Title: Forest stand dynamics modelling via SORTIE-ND
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Alana", "Clason", email = "alana.clason@bvcentre.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
            person("Sarah", "Last", role = "trl"))
Description: This package provides an R interface to the SORTIE-ND C++ model, allowing users to 
            model forest stand dynamics in an easy and reproducible way.
